---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy"
  description="Privacy notice for adrien.brage.fr - a privacy-respecting personal website."
>
  <article class="prose max-w-none">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-8">Privacy</h1>

    <p class="text-lg">This site respects your privacy.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Analytics</h2>
    <p>
      I use <a
        href="https://www.cloudflare.com/web-analytics/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare Web Analytics</a
      >, which:
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
      <li>Does not use cookies</li>
      <li>Does not track you across sites</li>
      <li>Does not collect personal information</li>
      <li>Complies with GDPR, CCPA, and PECR</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">No Third-Party Tracking</h2>
    <p>
      This site has no Google Analytics, no Facebook pixels, no ads, and no
      tracking scripts.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Hosting</h2>
    <p>
      This site is hosted on <a
        href="https://pages.cloudflare.com/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare Pages</a
      >. Cloudflare may collect basic access logs (IP address, user agent) for
      security and performance purposes. See{" "}
      <a
        href="https://www.cloudflare.com/privacypolicy/"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Cloudflare's privacy policy</a
      > for more details.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Images</h2>
    <p>
      Images are served from Cloudflare R2. No tracking or analytics are
      performed on image requests.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about privacy, reach out on{" "}
      <a
        href="https://twitter.com/AdrienBrault"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">Twitter</a
      > or{" "}
      <a
        href="https://github.com/adrienbrault"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer">GitHub</a
      >.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
